arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idAsaFollower)
	--Hydra.QActorWait(idAsaFollower, 1.5)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idAsaFollower)
	
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Asa_02a, idQuestOwner, idAsaFollower)
	--Hydra.QActorWait(idAsaFollower, 5.0)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idAsaFollower, conv_Asa_02a, true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idAsaFollower, 1.5)
end

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if Hydra.ActorHasItemByName(idSelf, item_AlimArmor) == false then
		idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
		
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
		
			if Hydra.IsPlayerVariableSet(idSelf, "QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AlimBarkHeard") == false then
				Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_Asa_01_AlimBark, idSelf, idAsaFollower)
				Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idSelf, "QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AlimBarkHeard")
			end
			
			Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idAsaFollower)		
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaAlim, "NPC_Run", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaAlim, true)
			Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idAsaFollower, "NPC_Idle_Kneel_HeadDown")
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
		Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(idAsaFollower)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idAsaFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idAsaFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if Hydra.ActorHasItemByName(idSelf, item_TalaArmor) == false then
		idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
		
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
			Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idAsaFollower)
			
			if Hydra.IsPlayerVariableSet(idSelf, "QST_Kehj_Armor_01_TalaBarkHeard") == false then
				Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_Asa_01_TalaBark, idSelf, idAsaFollower)
				Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idSelf, "QST_Kehj_Armor_01_TalaBarkHeard")
			end
			
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaTala, "NPC_Run", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaTala, true)
			Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idAsaFollower, "NPC_Idle_Kneel_HeadDown")
		end
	end	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
		Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(idAsaFollower)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idAsaFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idAsaFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idAsaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_AsaDungeonEntrance)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaClone, loc_DungeonEntrance, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idAsaClone, 1.5)
	end
end
